attributes.Long form description: The student is to change the Joy-Con controller to the comfort grip so he withdraws the Joy-Con from the Nintendo Switch and inserts it into the comfort grip. Then he withdraws the Joy-Con from the comfort grip and attaches the Joy-Con strap to each controller. The student removes the strap from the Joy-Con and inserts the Joy-Con back into the Nintendo Switch. He uses the kickstand to put it on the table and after that, he exchanges the game card from the console. Lastly, He wants to exchange the SD card but fails a couple of times trying to find the right slot, he finds the SD card slot and exchanges the SD Card.
